task_name: Convert Angular code to Vue code
query_example: Sample Angular -> VUE Query: Convert the following Angular component into a Vue.js component. The Angular component is a simple counter with buttons to increment and decrement the count. @Component({ selector: 'app-counter', template: '<button (click)="decrement()">-</button> {{ count }} <button (click)="increment()">+</button>', styles: [] }) export class CounterComponent { count: number = 0; increment() { this.count++; } decrement() { this.count--; } }
